      "time_str": "00:14.580",
      "text": "暖暖阳光懒懒爬进窗",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 20.99,
      "time_str": "00:20.990",
      "text": "悠悠微醺淡淡咖啡香",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 27.2,
      "time_str": "00:27.200",
      "text": "恍然你又在身旁",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
